snippet.title: Diana and Roma Halloween Candy Haul Stories
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma share some of their favorite Halloween candy haul stories. Tune in to find out what kind of candy they got, and hear about all the exciting Halloween adventures they went on!

00:00 Diana and Friends' Halloween Candy Adventure
07:10 Oliver and Mom Trick or Treat Preparations
12:47 Diana and Roma Trick or Treat Halloween Adventure
20:08 Diana and Roma Overcome Their Fears to Find Oliver
25:23 Diana and Roma Purple VS Orange Halloween Challenge
31:37 Roma's Mysterious Halloween Adventure

Thanks for watching!
